race.comment: MONI'S CHOICE (2) jumped from the squeeze on debut and ran an eye catching race, finishing second at this track over 520m (30.11). Likely to improve sharply this time. AGASSI (4) recorded a 3.5 lengths third in a Maiden last time 30.35 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. HUNTER (1) gets a chance to turn around his from the inside. Last time finished 6th on October 1 over 520m at this track behind Paid My Dues beaten 10 lengths (30.86) in a Maiden. Likely to be about the mark. CLEARY MAGIC (7) can play a role in the finish without surprising.
